#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/stylize/roberts.rst:21
msgid "Roberts"
msgstr "Roberts"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/stylize/roberts.rst:23
msgid ""
"This effect/filter applies the Roberts cross operator\\ [1]_ to the input "
"video stream. It detects edges (differential operator) and, in the default "
"settings, colors them white and grainy. Compare :ref:`effects-kirsch`, :ref:"
"`effects-prewitt` and :ref:`effects-sobel` effects."
msgstr ""
"Dit effect/filter past de Roberts cross operator\\ [1]_ toe op de "
"invoervideostream. Het detecteert randen (verschilbewerker) en, in de "
"standaard instellingen, kleurt ze wit en korrelig. Vergelijk de effecten :"
"ref:`effects-kirsch`, :ref:`effects-prewitt` en :ref:`effects-sobel`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/stylize/roberts.rst:25
msgid "The effect does not have keyframes."
msgstr "Dit effect heeft geen keyframes."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/stylize/roberts.rst:33
msgid "Roberts effect"
msgstr "Effect roberts"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/stylize/roberts.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Planes** - Set which :term:`planes<plane>` will be processed, unprocessed "
"planes will be copied. Default is **YUV**."
msgstr ""
"**Vlakken** - stelt in welke :term:`vlakken<plane>` bewerkt zullen worden, "
"niet bewerkte vlakken zullen gekopieerd worden. Standaard is **YUV**."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/stylize/roberts.rst:37
msgid "**Scale** - Set value which will be multiplied with filtered result"
msgstr ""
"**Schaal** - stelt de waarde in die vermenigvuldigt zal worden met gefilterd "
"resultaat"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/stylize/roberts.rst:39
msgid "**Delta** - Set value which will be added to filtered result"
msgstr ""
"**Delta** - stelt de waarde in die opgeteld wordt bij het gefilterde "
"resultaat"

